ability%20shields.&amp;rft.identifier=https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fabstract%3D4213674&amp;rft.aufirst=Alan%20Z.&amp;rft.aulast=Rozenshtein&amp;rft.au=Alan%20Z.%20Rozenshtein&amp;rft.date=2022-11-23&amp;rft.language=en"></span></p>
